# Database Conventions

- Primary keys are TEXT — UUIDs for projects, sequential `DEF-XXX` for deficiencies
- Enum fields must have CHECK constraints listing every valid value
- JSON arrays stored as TEXT with DEFAULT `'[]'` (e.g., `photo_paths`)
- Timestamps are TEXT in ISO format using `DEFAULT (datetime('now'))`
- Foreign keys use REFERENCES and are enforced via `PRAGMA foreign_keys = ON`
- When modifying schema: update `schema.sql`, update `setup.ts` seed data, re-run `npm run setup`
- Seed data should be realistic construction industry content spanning all enum values

See `db/CLAUDE.md` for full conventions.
